    "Moreover, algorithms themselves require the tuning of a large number of parameters, and determining the quantity and range of these parameters is a problem that cannot be directly described by mathematical theory.",
    "It requires researchers to rely more on their \"experience\" to debug them.",
    "Transfer learning (TL) [248] is one possible direction that could address this problem.",
    "It leverages the similarity between data, tasks, or models to transfer previously learned knowledge to new scenarios.",
    "Additionally, Multi-Modal Machine Learning (MMML) [249], [250] can integrate various types of information, such as images, videos, and text, to process multimodal information from multiple sources."
  ],
